# Changelog

## 03/30/2026

### Added
- Add Vendored Libraries for Port
### Changed
- 64 Bit conversion
  - Use [id-software/DOOM/pull/2](https://github.com/id-Software/DOOM/pull/2)
  - Use [id-software/DOOM/pull/9](https://github.com/id-Software/DOOM/pull/9)
- Changed Fire to LCTRL instead of RCTRL
### Removed
- Remove X11 in Favor of SDL3 Video API
- Removed Sound Server stuff in Favor of SDL3 Audio API
  - SDL3_mixer coming soon
- Remove Some Linux Specific Code
  - Note: Made on a M3 Max MacBook Pro.
- Remove Certain `#ifdef NORMALLINUX` and `#ifdef LINUX` checks
### Issues
- Due to Input handling being changed some functions are broken
- All sfx are at full volume.(Haven't figured out how to increase or decrease volume ingame)